  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tactical Mission: Target Rush</strong> is a minimalist, but immersive, single-player target shooting experience. Challenge yourself as you chase for best scores rushing through close quarters battle courses with dynamic targets that test your skills and push you to the limit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >TARGET SHOOTING</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into authentic and immersive gunplay as you navigate the layouts. Be tactical – targets and zombies dynamically change each round, demanding quick adaptation. Stay sharp and avoid detection as the difficulty ramps up, pushing you to master your environment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895350/extras/8f0bc5e5612ed69db1a1e195eb45a579.poster.avif?t=1746544843\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895350/extras/8f0bc5e5612ed69db1a1e195eb45a579.webm?t=1746544843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895350/extras/8f0bc5e5612ed69db1a1e195eb45a579.mp4?t=1746544843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAME MODES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a range of thrilling modes, each designed to test your skills in unique ways:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>RESCUE</strong><br>Take on the ultimate challenge. Disarm the bomb, save the hostage, and outwit relentless enemy AI determined to stop you at every turn.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>TARGET RUSH</strong><br>Sharpen your reflexes in a fast-paced scenario where split-second decisions matter. Identify threats, avoid civilians, and stay sharp as enemy targets can spot and reset you.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>GUN & RUN</strong><br>Perfect your aim and movement in this training mode. With no threats to worry about, it's the ideal way to refine your skills—though unlocking rewards isn't part of the mission.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ZOMBIE</strong><br>Survival meets precision. As you dodge relentless zombies, focus on neutralizing enemy targets while avoiding civilian casualties. Keep moving, stay alert, and prove your mastery under pressure.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895350/extras/1b9be51440a613b651792e4af6d28ef6.poster.avif?t=1746544843\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895350/extras/1b9be51440a613b651792e4af6d28ef6.webm?t=1746544843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895350/extras/1b9be51440a613b651792e4af6d28ef6.mp4?t=1746544843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PROGRESSION</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expand your arsenal of weapons as you master the game. Choose from a small selection of rifles, pistols, and shotguns.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895350/extras/8a3929942f42267d95ad837e1f267617.poster.avif?t=1746544843\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895350/extras/8a3929942f42267d95ad837e1f267617.webm?t=1746544843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895350/extras/8a3929942f42267d95ad837e1f267617.mp4?t=1746544843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ENVIRONMENTS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock new maps as you progress, each providing a unique set of encounters and presenting new tactical situations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895350/extras/4ce92ceb1021f273a77cad06d4db10f9.poster.avif?t=1746544843\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895350/extras/4ce92ceb1021f273a77cad06d4db10f9.webm?t=1746544843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895350/extras/4ce92ceb1021f273a77cad06d4db10f9.mp4?t=1746544843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
